      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "CN Pool: Shared (Warehouse \"default\")\nServes: Tenant A, B, C\n\n  3 x CN nodes\n  8 CPU / 32 GB each\n  200 GB SSD local cache\n  K8s HPA: scale 3→8 on CPU > 70%",
