      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "CN Pool: Dedicated (Warehouse \"tenant_x\")\nServes: Tenant X only\n\n  4 x CN nodes\n  16 CPU / 64 GB each\n  500 GB SSD local cache\n  K8s HPA: scale 4→16 on CPU > 60%",
